result-*

# The compiled CLI binary (built into ./review-skills by `go build`).
# Anchored with a leading slash so it does NOT match the package source
# directory name `review-skills/` higher in the tree.
/review-skills

# The repo-root .gitignore ignores any `audit/` directory (the Plan-B
# metrics output). Re-include this package's internal/audit Go package.
!internal/audit/
